dct_title_s: A complete map of the southern continent : survey'd by Capt. Abel Tasman & depicted by order of the East India Company in Halland [sic] in the Stadt House at Amsterdam
dct_description_sm: Shows Australasia and New Guinea. In upper right corner: Vol. 1, page 325. An English version of the first state of the map in Melchisédec Thévenot, Relations de divers voyages curieux ... Paris : Thomas Moette, 1663. cf. Perry, T.M. A guide to maps of Australia in books published 1780-1830. From: Navigantium atque itinerantium bibliotheca ... / John Harris. -- London : T. Woodward, 1744-1748.
